item.name: Kadhi
item.desc: Kadhi is a popular Indian dish with a tangy yogurt-based curry. It is often paired with pakoras (deep-fried fritters) and served over steamed rice. The creamy texture and delightful blend of spices, including turmeric and cumin, make kadhi a comforting and satisfying meal. Its unique flavor profile is a true culinary delight.

item.name: Chole
item.desc: Chola is a popular South Indian dish made from black chickpeas simmered in a flavorful blend of spices, onions, tomatoes, and coconut. It is typically served with steamed rice, dosa, or chapati. This hearty and protein-rich dish has a rich and aromatic taste, perfect for a satisfying meal.

item.name: Rajma
item.desc: Made from red kidney beans cooked in a flavorful tomato-based gravy. It is seasoned with a blend of spices and often served with rice or roti. Rajma is known for its rich and hearty taste, making it a comforting and nutritious meal.

item.name: Tawa Roti
item.desc: Tawa roti is a popular Indian bread made by kneading wheat flour, water and a pinch of salt. It is then rolled into thin dish and cooked on a hot tawa. The result is a delicious slightly crispy roti with a soft and chewy texture, perfect for pairing with curries or enjoying on its own.

item.name: Tawa Butter Roti
item.desc: It boasts a golden brown, flaky exterior and a butter melt in your mouth texture. This aromatic delicacy is perfect for savoring with curries or enjoying on its own.

item.name: Plain Paratha

item.name: 5 Poori

item.name: Aloo Paratha
item.desc: Aloo paratha is a popular Indian flatbread stuffed with a flavorful filling of mashed potatoes, aromatic spices and herbs. The dough is rolled out and cooked on a griddle until golden and crispy.

item.name: Pyaaz Paratha
item.desc: Pyaaz paratha is a delectable Indian flatbread stuffed with a generous filling of finely chopped onion. The dough is skillfully rolled out and cooked until golden brown, imparting a delightful crispness.

item.name: Gobi Paratha
item.desc: Aloo paratha is a popular Indian flatbread stuffed with a flavorful filling of mashed potato, aromatic spices and herbs. The dough is rolled out and cooked on a griddle until golden and crispy.

item.name: Mixed Paratha
item.desc: The dough is skillfully blended with a medley of spices, vegetables, and herbs, creating a mouthwatering symphony of taste. With its crispy exterior and soft interior, each bite offers a delightful fusion of textures and a burst of enticing flavors.

item.name: Jeera Rice
item.desc: The rice is cooked to perfection, resulting in separate grains with a subtle aroma and a hint of earthy, warm flavors. It pairs well with various curries and adds a delightful touch to any meal.

item.name: Kadhi Chawal
item.desc: The tangy kadhi is made with gram flour, spices and tempered with aromatic tadka. Served over fluffy rice, it offers a delightful combination of flavors, textures and a comforting meal experience.

item.name: Rajma Chawal
item.desc: Served with steamed basmati rice, it creates a harmonious blend of textures and tastes, resulting in a comforting and satisfying meal.

item.name: Chole Chawal
item.desc: The rice is fluffy and fragrant, while the curry is rich and flavorful infused with a blend of spices like cumin, coriander and turmeric.

item.name: Tea
item.desc: Made with milk, tea leaves and sugar boiled to perfect aromatic colour and give you a perfect refreshing feeling.
